---
---

<section class="py-24 md:py-32">
  <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-6 text-center">
    <div class="mb-6">
      <img src="/img/logo-kosei.svg" alt="AI克塞号 Logo" class="hero-breathe w-20 h-20 rounded-2xl mx-auto mb-6 border border-[var(--color-border)] shadow-lg" />
    </div>
    <p class="text-sm text-[var(--color-brand-light)] tracking-[0.2em] uppercase mb-3">Time-Aware AI Engineering</p>
    <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-6xl font-bold tracking-tight mb-4 brand-display text-[var(--color-text)] hero-wave">
      <span style="--i:0">A</span><span style="--i:1">I</span><span style="--i:2">克</span><span style="--i:3">塞</span><span style="--i:4">号</span>
      <span class="hero-wave-gap" style="--i:5"> / </span>
      <span style="--i:6">A</span><span style="--i:7">I</span><span class="hero-wave-gap" style="--i:8"> </span><span style="--i:9">K</span><span style="--i:10">o</span><span style="--i:11">s</span><span style="--i:12">e</span><span style="--i:13">i</span>
    </h1>
    <p class="text-lg text-[var(--color-text-secondary)] max-w-2xl mx-auto mb-8">
      以时间感知驱动智能工程，专注 AI 场景化落地与高可靠架构实践。
    </p>
    <div class="flex items-center justify-center gap-4 flex-wrap">
      <a href="/blog/" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-5 py-2.5 rounded-lg bg-[var(--color-brand)] text-white text-sm hover:opacity-90 transition-opacity">
        进入博客
      </a>
      <a href="https://github.com/GuanXcode" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-4 py-2 rounded-lg border border-[var(--color-border)] text-sm text-[var(--color-text-secondary)] hover:text-[var(--color-text)] hover:border-[var(--color-brand)] transition-all">
        GitHub
      </a>
      <a href="mailto:guanx214@gmail.com" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-4 py-2 rounded-lg border border-[var(--color-border)] text-sm text-[var(--color-text-secondary)] hover:text-[var(--color-text)] hover:border-[var(--color-brand)] transition-all">
        Email
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .hero-wave > span {
    display: inline-block;
    animation: heroWave 1.9s ease-in-out infinite;
    animation-delay: calc(var(--i) * 0.08s);
  }

  .hero-breathe {
    animation: heroBreathe 2.8s ease-in-out infinite;
  }

  .hero-wave-gap {
    margin: 0 0.08em;
  }

  @keyframes heroBreathe {
    0%, 100% {
      filter: brightness(1) saturate(100%);
      box-shadow: 0 8px 20px rgba(2, 132, 199, 0.16);
    }

    50% {
      filter: brightness(1.08) saturate(112%);
      box-shadow: 0 10px 28px rgba(6, 182, 212, 0.3);
    }
  }

  @keyframes heroWave {
    0%, 100% {
      transform: translateY(0);
    }

    25% {
      transform: translateY(-2px);
    }

    50% {
      transform: translateY(1px);
    }

    75% {
      transform: translateY(-1px);
    }
  }
</style>
